#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the "Start with" section of route ordering</h2>
The "Start with" section is an ordered list of stops that the driver will
make before performing any of the rest of the route.  This order is
specified exactly and not optimized for time by the software.  This section
will always contain the start of the route, the distribution center.
